Zouma is yet to win a senior cap for his country but has represented France at various levels including a stint as U21 captain.

There are also call-ups for a host of other fellow French Premier League players including Hugo Lloris, Laurent Koscielny, Mamadou Sakho, Morgan Schneiderlin, Moussa Sissoko and Olivier Giroud.

Manchester City defender Bacary Sagna is also given the nod by Deschamp despite enduring a stop-start season for the Citizens.

Goalkeepers: Lloris (Tottenham Hotspur), Mandanda (Marseille), Ruffier (Saint-Etienne).

Defenders: Evra (Juventus), Jallet (Lyon), Koscielny (Arsenal), Sagna (Manchester City), Sakho (Liverpool), Trmmoulinas (Sevilla), Varane (Real Madrid), Zouma (Chelsea).

Midfielders: Gonalons (Lyon), Kondogbia (Monaco), Matuidi (Paris Saint-Germain), Payet (Marseille), Schneiderlin (Southampton), Sissoko (Newcastle United).

Forwards: Benzema (Real Madrid), Fekir (Lyon), Giroud (Arsenal), Griezmann (Atletico Madrid), Lacazette (Lyon), Valbuena (Dynamo Moscow).

